, said the UK Department of Health and Social Care.  UPDATE on coronavirus (#COVID19) testing in the UK:   As of 9am 4 March 2020, a total of 16,659 people have been tested:   16,574 negative.  85 positive.   For latest information visit:  ▶️ https://t.co/CZh5JdyN2Q pic.twitter.com/Zlu9TSBUwH 
